          <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 36px;">Apuleius The Golden Ass and <br>Other Philosophical Writings</span></p>
          <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 36px;"><br><i>Translated by Thomas Taylor</i></span></p>
